25:45.000 --> 25:47.048
<i>That made my life
what it is</i>

25:47.120 --> 25:48.246
Hal?

25:51.520 --> 25:54.046
It's 10:00.
We gotta go.

25:54.640 --> 25:57.530
What are
you talking about?

25:57.600 --> 26:00.001
Hal, we gotta go
do that thing.

26:01.000 --> 26:03.128
You know, at the place.

26:03.200 --> 26:04.850
What thing?

26:06.080 --> 26:07.730
Hey, sorry, ladies.

26:07.800 --> 26:09.928
I gotta steal your
dance partner here.

26:10.000 --> 26:11.570
No!

26:11.640 --> 26:12.721
What are you doing?

26:12.840 --> 26:13.966
