26:14.040 --> 26:15.246
From what?

26:15.320 --> 26:16.526
From what!

26:17.080 --> 26:21.130
<i>Oh, rainfalls and hard times coming,
they won't leave me tonight</i>

26:21.680 --> 26:24.604
From a pack of stampeding buffalo!
That's from what!

26:25.800 --> 26:30.761
<i>Just do let this spirit
survive Everybody's dancing</i>

26:30.840 --> 26:32.683
Come join us. I'm going
after the redhead.

26:32.760 --> 26:34.171
You can have your
pick of the other two.

26:36.160 --> 26:39.846
You mean you get the hyena, and I choose
between the hippo and the giraffe?

26:40.600 --> 26:43.729
Don't be intimidated, man.
They don't bite! Now, let's go!

26:43.800 --> 26:45.086
