27:44.520 --> 27:48.844
<i>In the sky the birds
are pulling rain</i>

27:50.920 --> 27:55.084
<i>In your life a curse
has got a name</i>

27:57.920 --> 27:59.570
Building a parachute?

28:01.280 --> 28:02.327
Excuse me?

28:03.040 --> 28:04.849
They're a little big,
aren't they?

28:06.440 --> 28:11.401
Oh, I get it. You ripped the
spinnaker on your sailboat, right?

28:17.600 --> 28:18.681
I'm sorry. I just...

28:18.800 --> 28:23.169
It seemed so funny seeing someone like
you holding up a pair of old-lady trou.

28:23.240 --> 28:25.208
Someone like me?

28:25.280 --> 28:27.726
Yeah. You know,
someone so fit.

28:29.200 --> 28:31.089
