28:33.640 --> 28:36.041
Miss, please. I'm sorry.

28:36.120 --> 28:38.122
I didn't mean to offend you.

28:38.200 --> 28:43.047
Hey, unibrow, why don't you double
your dosage and leave me alone?

28:43.120 --> 28:45.248
Let's start over.

28:45.320 --> 28:48.244
Look, that was
really dumb of me.

28:48.320 --> 28:52.245
You were probably buying 'em for someone
close to you, right? And I insulted them.

28:52.320 --> 28:53.970
Well, however it is
you took it,

28:54.040 --> 28:55.804
I want you to know I didn't
mean to piss you off.

28:55.920 --> 28:59.208
I wanted to meet you,
and I guess...

29:00.680 --> 29:02.842
