smooth sometimes.

29:04.240 --> 29:06.891
Let me make it up to you.

29:06.960 --> 29:09.930
Excuse me, miss.
Is everything all right?

29:20.120 --> 29:24.762
So, what do you do
for a living, Rosemary?

29:24.840 --> 29:27.969
