at the hospital right now,

29:28.040 --> 29:32.887
'cause I'm waiting for this
re-up thing to come through.

29:33.000 --> 29:36.209
Re-up? What,
are you in the army?

29:37.760 --> 29:39.364
Peace Corps.

29:39.440 --> 29:40.680
Peace Corps.

29:40.760 --> 29:43.411
That's very altrudocious
of you.

29:43.480 --> 29:45.801
Altrudocious?
That's not a word.

29:47.360 --> 29:50.682
You mean
humanidocious, right?

29:52.440 --> 29:53.646
Yeah. That's the one.

29:53.720 --> 29:56.371
All right.
Ready to order?

29:56.480 --> 30:01.805
