31:46.640 --> 31:47.721
All right, then.

31:47.840 --> 31:49.410
Rosemary, you sure
you're okay?

31:49.480 --> 31:53.121
Yeah. I'm a little
embarrassed but

31:53.200 --> 31:55.043
